\newlabel{fig:pareto_sota_obliv_floor}{{1}{8}{Floor-distance win-margin (\TanGCE {} $-$ Obliviator) per panel under control-damage budgets $\Delta Y \in \{1, 3, 5, 10\}$ pp. Each row is one (model, concept) panel; positive (blue) = \TanGCE {} closer to floor. Tie band $\pm 5$pp shaded}{figure.caption.21}{}}
